@{B}Aasimon, Scild, General Ecology:@{UB}@{PAR}

Scilds are on good terms with other @{" aasimon " LINK "ImpPro:Data/ExtMonsterData/Aasimon, General.long/main"}, especially movanic devas. These
devas will often lead groups of @{" scilds " LINK "ImpPro:Data/ExtMonsterData/Aasimon, General.long/main"} on important missions for the cause of
good.@{PAR}

